{"id": "1337259933476851815", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "다시 봐도 이격 돌 전용 명륜, 장난아닌데요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:13:33.229000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337260185915228161", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "주옵이 광기회복, 부옵은 착용자의 광기회복, 독, 생명회복이 10% 증가, 착용자 광기폭발시에 소비한 광기의 20%를 돌려받음.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:14:33.415000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337260298322710579", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "거기에 이격 돌은 광기폭발로 아군전체 광기15 증가, 초한돌파시에 30증가.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:15:00.215000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337260421803016253", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "연산불가능+저 명륜 하게 되면 광기폭발 돌아가는게 미쳐돌아갈거 같은데.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:15:29.655000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337261955303477359", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "성위의 장, 룰이 엄청 많이 바뀌는데요?", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:21:35.270000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337262050954707027", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "타비, 성위에선 쓰기 힘들지도 모르겠습니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:21:58.075000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337262201198612540", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "최대 컴퓨팅 파워 : 전투에서 어떤 방법을 사용하든 컴퓨팅 파워 한계는 10을 돌파할수 없습니다. 초과시, 컴퓨팅 파워 1포인트는 모든 각성한 각성체의 광기 2포인트로 전환됩니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:22:33.896000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337262282484482138", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "즉, 10일때 아이디어 카드 쓰게 되면 11로 올라가는게 아니라 광기 2포인트 올라가게 됨", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:22:53.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337262643022663712", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "명령 광란 : 한라운드에 명령카드 10장을 플레이하게 되면 플레이된 명령 카드 한장당 \"광란\" 레벨 1을 얻습니다. 광란은 이 라운드 동안 플레이된 각 명령 카드마다 최대 생명력의 2%를 잃게 합니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:24:19.235000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337262708537688126", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "한턴에 카드 10장 이상씩 쓴다면 피가 깎이게 됨", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:24:34.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337263117687722085", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "조금씩 패치중인거 같은데... 피가 깎이는게 아니라 카드의 컴퓨팅 파워를 증가시키네요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:26:12.404000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337263345270657075", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "뭐, 타비는 은열쇠에너지로 2~6익 날리니까 아주 못쓸정도는 아니려나.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:27:06.664000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337270632345505792", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "융해 돌 능력을 깔끔하게 번역해봤는데 이거 완전히 사기네요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:56:04.038000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337270655242080277", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "어제 번역 잘못한것도 몇개 있었고.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:56:09.497000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337270931466354770", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "특히 3돌이 완전히 돌았습니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:57:15.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337271070671110145", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "기본타격, 기본방어가 일단 광기10 얻고, \"추가로 광기 상한의 5%에 해당하는 광기\"를 얻는거였어요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:57:48.543000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337271206487003147", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "광기 상한이 기본적으로 초한 안시키면 100, 초한 시키면 200이니까.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:58:20.924000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337271237109481495", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "5 or 10을 추가로 받는것임.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:58:28.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337271463119556741", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "광기 상한이 200, 400이었나.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:59:22.110000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337271517016490015", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "젠장. 헷갈리는군요", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T03:59:34.960000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337274656511627275", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "종말 10레벨이면 독이 200%씩 들어가는군요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T04:12:03.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337274747183960306", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "아니네, 추가로 200%니까, 300%, 3배로 들어가는구만....", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T04:12:25.092000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337284479122935910", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "자.... 이제 문제는 이번 이격 돌에 어느정도를 투자할것인가인데.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T04:51:05.367000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337284489432531028", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "고민되네요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T04:51:07.825000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
