{"id": "1337300891845398559", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "성위의 장에서만 적용되는 고유룰이 적용된다고 합니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:56:18.465000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337300912770650165", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "932970987274793000", "author_name": "lurvi_", "author_bot": false, "content": "명령 카드라 적혀있네요", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:56:23.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337300952905941054", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "아, 그건 그거고, 저건 저거임. ㅋㅋㅋ", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:56:33.023000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301007130034186", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "최대 컴퓨팅 파워 제한은 적용되고", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:56:45.951000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301042425106483", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "한턴 사용한 카드 제한은 또 따로 적용임.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:56:54.366000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301087228530711", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "지금 테스트 중이고 조금씩 바뀌고는 있다는데", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:57:05.048000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301145122508921", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "컴퓨팅 파워랑 카드 사용량 제한은 둘다 적용될거 같습니다.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:57:18.851000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301678646624297", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "일단 전용 명륜 3돌은 뽑고 시작해야할거 같고.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:59:26.053000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337301730383237142", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "이격 돌을 얼마나 뽑아야할지가 관건이네요.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T05:59:38.388000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337334051241070662", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "그나저나 이격 돌을 넣어서 어떤 팟을 짜야할까요. 중독캐랑 조합해야할거 같은데.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T08:08:04.281000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1337334127908622387", "channel_id": "1300659495550062592", "type": 0, "author_id": "145502316647153664", "author_name": "banadil", "author_bot": false, "content": "이격 돌, 릴리는 넣는게 좋을거 같고.", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T08:08:22.560000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
